257
00:17:11,420 --> 00:17:15,470
Karena ponsel ini tampaknya
menggunakan kunci sidik jari...

258
00:17:15,740 --> 00:17:17,250
Permisi.

259
00:17:19,350 --> 00:17:20,870
Kami akan meminjam jari korban.

260
00:17:24,470 --> 00:17:27,350
Dia jelas menerima sebuah pesan tadi.

261
00:17:27,970 --> 00:17:30,110
Mari kita lihat. Apa katanya?

262
00:17:30,280 --> 00:17:35,900
